	<p>
		This is a free product that I made for myself but thought others could
		benefit from. This means that you are deciding to use pushbroom at your own
		risk and will not hold me liable if anything goes wrong. That being said the
		only assurance I can give you is that since I am using this, if anything
		goes terribly wrong, it went wrong for me too. You can always stop using
		pushbroom by following the instructions from Google
		<%= link_to 'here', 'http://www.google.com/support/accounts/bin/answer.py?hl=en&answer=41236' %>.
	</p>
</div>